0001	Tip: Attacking from the back increases your hit rate!
0002	Tip: Use the different Elements to gain an advantage! Refer to the element table during combat!
0003	Tip: Job Lv Up to increase your Unit’s stats and gain new Abilities!
0004	Tip: Equip Equipment to increase your Unit’s job level!
0005	Tip: Equipment are consumed upon Job Lv Up!
0006	Tip: Customise Unit Abilities in Ability Setup!
0007	Tip: Evolve a unit to increase its max level and max job level!
0008	Tip: Evolution Materials can be found in Golem Games, Goddess Worship and Alchemia Hunt!
0009	Tip: Use soul shards to Limit Break your units!
0010	Tip: Limit Break to increase your unit’s max level limit and unlock more Job Classes for your unit!
0011	Tip: Get different Job Tokens at Event Trials!
0012	Tip: Master a Job Class by fully equipping your unit at Job Lv 11!
0013	Tip: Use Alchemia Pots to Upgrade your equipment!
0014	Tip: Further improve your Units with different Gears! 
0015	Tip: Upgrade your Gears to maximize their potential!
0016	Tip: Use Ores to Upgrade your Gears!
0017	Tip: Need More Zeni? Enter the Gold Rush Dungeon!
0018	Tip: Earn more gems by completing Story Milestones and Daily Missions!